2008-08-03 18:36:01 GMT	Carlo Contavalli <ccontavalli@masobit.net>	patch-74

    Summary:
      fixed bug in local:// handling, and updated docs.
    Revision:
      modxslt2--main--1.3--patch-74

    * lib/modxslt-doc.c - fixed bug in local:// handling that
      seldom caused segmentation faults and wrong behaviors.
    
    * doc/faq/faq.xml - updated, to clarify description of
      local://.
    
    * doc/faq/xslt/faq-fo.xsl - the world has changed, the .xsl
      was making recent versions of fop and xsltproc unhappy.
      Updated the stylesheet.
    
    * doc/faq/xslt/faq-html.xsl - same as above.
    
    * doc/faq/* - regenerated all the output files.

    modified files:
