      Source maintainance for newer systems.
    Revision:
      modxslt2--main--1.3--patch-71

    * ChangeLog - added a ChangeLog file generated
      directly by TLA with all revisions.
    
    * */Makefile.in - modified to infer --tag parameter
      for libtool explicitly. This should fix a long
      lasting bug with newer autoconf versions.
    
